name: A postcard from Pondicherry
description: This was captured to show the architecture in Pondicherry and how the poppy colours, the aesthetic gate, the bi-cycle and every other element in the picture adds up to make the view more beautiful.  Artist - Sagar Narula Colour grading software - Adobe Lightroom Location - Pondicherry, India Resolution - 3480x4640 Date - September 13th, 2019
